Howto install nmrename:
-----------------------

Dependencies:
- ANSI C Compiler (tested with gcc>=4.2.2)
- make
- coreutils


Installation:
- `make`
- `make [OPTIONS] install`

OPTIONS:
PREFIX=<prefix>   : prefix where nmrename will be installed (default: /usr)
DESTDIR=<destdir> : Destination directory. You can define an alternate root
                    path. (Important for packagers)


Uninstall:
- `make [OPTIONS] uninstall`
